{"tid":855253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港近年多左咁多野豬，好多謝呢班香港野豬關注組既動保撚","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T12:30:52.000Z","uid":190431,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f12cf18bced0c6d1a94e1fb3695573b7e204fb9","tid":855253,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/wildboarconcerngroup/?locale2=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwildboarconcerngroup%2F%3Flocale2%3Dzh_HK&d=vWSirjpo6HHfdCpzl4aijiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a976de7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/wildboarconcerngroup/?locale2=zh_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n野豬係由普通養豬變成，因為豬有獸性一走到大自然就會由長毛長遼牙，而且具攻擊性。<br />\n但班野豬保護撚，話要親近大自然反對殺野豬。<br />\n野豬傷人又可以反指責係人嚇親佢哋，野豬破壞性又比野狗大得多。<br />\n<br />\n成班圍爐，自我感覺良好又出書拎光環"},{"pid":"dfdb0914862b823f49d52fd32f35c377f9ecd408","tid":855253,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得嗰篇叫人唔好主動搞啲動物嗰篇文言文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc3938d0492d53c04034b02991a48bd3b788884","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n動保撚同環保撚一樣慷他人之慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7932fa772d2bf34f9e5f501c6bb99f3ae88b2b1b","tid":855253,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.tanews.org.tw/info/7425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tanews.org.tw%2Finfo%2F7425&d=vWSirjpo6HHfdCpzl4aijiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9052dcd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tanews.org.tw/info/7425</a>"},{"pid":"1d1914e4198c786f451421de5a565044529a877e","tid":855253,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:35:43.000Z","msg":"台南市一位住楠西山區的蔡姓農民說，兩年前他的豬舍跑丟了一隻養了4個多月的黑豬，自認倒楣外也無計可施。一年前，他養的狗群在豬舍附近圍著一隻「山豬」狂吠，乍看之下嚇了一跳，但山豬背部一塊造形狀特殊的白毛斑點，讓他印象深刻：那不是我的黑豬嗎？怎會變成野豬模樣？而獠牙最讓他驚恐，因為飼養的情感，他喚回狗群讓豬逃命。<br />\n<br />\n這謎團直到他看了電視播出國家地理雜誌才釋疑，原來，豬對環境的適應力超強，家豬只要逃到大自然半年後，體型即開始「野化」成為獵食性動物。體型變得筆直、腹部縮小，贅肉減少、腿也變長，如此讓牠奔跑速度加快，可以追捕獵物或逃避被獵殺；常用嘴鼻挖掘竹筍、番薯等地下根莖，會讓鼻子變得筆直；而長出獠牙以利挖掘及攻擊防衛。動物學家還發現一對家豬只要在外繁衍三代，子孫就成為野豬。"},{"pid":"fd0ecca2227183f34ff701eb429acfad209f5862","tid":855253,"uid":190431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"蔡姓農民趕快叫兒子上網搜索「家豬變野豬」關鍵字，找到諸多實例証實專家的說法，例如日本福島核災後，許多農民飼養的家豬從豬舍跑走，災民重建家園之餘，發現野豬數量爆增，研判就是家豬野化而成，或是家豬與當地野豬交配產下「野家豬」，大批豬群跑到農田大肆破壞，讓福島縣政府傷透腦筋。<br />\n<br />\n目前澳洲數量龐大的野豬，也是早期由英國人在1788年左右帶入飼養的家豬野化而成。<br />\n<br />\n而小山豬一旦被養在豬舍，飯來張口，長大後獠牙不明顯，不是典型的野豬模樣，蔡姓農民從自己的飼養經驗得到証實。原來，他在農閒時期常帶著獵犬捕捉山豬「為民除害」，賣山豬肉也是一筆收入，獵得成豬後，尚未離乳的仔豬就帶回家養，養山豬也是山區居民的副業。養在豬舍就是家豬，野放山林就是野豬，豬對環境的適應力太強了。"},{"pid":"12fe81b767f0418f0603d756d29243370f21a0ef","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n城市論壇講緊野豬,嗰個村長講自己條村啲野豬襲擊人都有十幾單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動保撚去曬邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6072f11b9c7782bf306a062136d66f0ea35e5965","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c870365cf571a9364c317f7f6e067101e39b8459","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇新聞見到野豬隊要解散,動保撚開香檳未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後野豬冇曬天敵,可以橫行霸道,到時佢哋咪有得瘋狂同野豬相遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae189d676c6d31984d1e1de6a6fae81550a092d","tid":855253,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"請問點樣可以合法獵，？"},{"pid":"7d17c04ac0a2800f21d929aa0e07bdb205cecb78","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ae189d676c6d31984d1e1de6a6fae81550a092d","tid":855253,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"請問點樣可以合法獵，？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"呢層唔清楚,但記得70年代,賭王都仲有喺香港打獵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b50d1ce0fb3f2bc130013b5ed11f43c5f831428","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:45:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06cd9fc67c23c25128c09e382dacdd5474663c6c","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e858f128e7d04d286efa2f6b2a454d0798ad35","tid":855253,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0DsJ1na.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0DsJ1na.jpg&h=2407517b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x4sKTko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fx4sKTko.png&h=38d38baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YEtAH0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYEtAH0s.jpg&h=02f194bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B54nFUr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB54nFUr.png&h=0d82df80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/66sVPci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F66sVPci.jpg&h=be0e16a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NRGICPZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com